name: Justin P. Rohrer
content: Justin P. Rohrer's Academic & Research Homepage Justin P. Rohrer, Ph.D. Dr. Justin P. Rohrer is currently an Assistant Professor of Computer Science and leads the Tactical Networked Communications Architecture Design (TaNCAD) Lab at the Naval Postgraduate School (NPS) in Monterey, CA. He is an expert in IPv6, large-scale Internet measurement, and cloud system architectures. © 1999–2025 Justin P. Rohrer, all rights reserved.
